---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy & Cookies Policy | Tools Nestt">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-24 px-6 prose prose-invert">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-black italic text-white uppercase mb-8 tracking-tighter">Privacy & Cookies</h1>
    
    <h2 class="text-white border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">1. Data Controller</h2>
    <p>Tools Nestt ("we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains how we process data when you use our website builder and hosting services.</p>

    <h2 class="text-white border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect essential information to provide the service:
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li><strong>Account Data:</strong> Email address and authentication identifiers.</li>
        <li><strong>Deployment Data:</strong> HTML, CSS, JS, and static assets uploaded to R2.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Data:</strong> Handled entirely by Paddle. We do not store credit card numbers.</li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-white border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">3. Third-Party Data Processors</h2>
    <p>We share data with the following essential providers:
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
        <li><strong>Cloudflare Inc:</strong> For hosting infrastructure, DDoS protection, and SSL (Data stored in US-West).</li>
        <li><strong>Paddle:</strong> For global tax compliance and payment security.</li>
        <li><strong>Google:</strong> For Analytics and targeted advertising (AdSense/Ads).</li>
      </ul>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-white border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">4. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to maintain your session and analyze traffic. By using our site, you consent to the use of cookies for personalized advertising and performance tracking. You can manage cookie preferences in your browser settings.</p>

    <h2 class="text-white border-b border-slate-800 pb-2">5. AI Policy</h2>
    <p>Our AI tools utilize third-party Large Language Models. We do not use your proprietary code or hosted data to train these models. Input data for AI generation is processed ephemerally.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>
